### File Naming Recommendation

Current filenames have issues:
- "balck" typo
- Spaces in filenames (not best practice)
- Inconsistent capitalization

**Recommended Rename**:
```bash
# Current → Recommended
"Hadosh Academy logo balck background.png" → "hadosh-logo-dark.png"
"Hadosh academy no background.png" → "hadosh-logo-transparent.png"
"big image of constructors building claude code logo.png" → "hero-construction-illustration.png"
```

**Benefits**:
- No spaces (better for web)
- Descriptive and clear
- Lowercase convention
- Purpose-driven naming

